Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:56.36,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}踏山·世界的邊際
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:15.78,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 彼方的假日·梳發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備前進 上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:45.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵機 準備發射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離800
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填手 彈種裝填榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:05.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 通知後續部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀一輛 跟上我隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:22.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀一輛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西婭 克勞斯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真變得精神了啊 守子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:07.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷都好了 還粘我們 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這裡很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱 還那麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部送來的 麻煩簽收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:28.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的是私人信件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在 我在我在在在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄給你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽寄給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 你的還是那位教授同志寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授同志？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓教名授同志 賽普特州常見的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\an8}賽普特：Spet，法語的7，另外本作的舞台賽茲(Seize)是法語中的16。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小授同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遠的地方也有你的朋友 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:23.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊 小乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真相信了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給克勞斯送份禮物去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:47.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·的·常·客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 司令部怎麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克…克勞斯少校閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 謝謝泥滴管照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 那是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 留守就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留守？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你武運昌盛 二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 明天去遠足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 真好啊 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠足…菲莉西婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是遠足 僅僅是走路的話也太沒趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不如來玩個遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽茲南部的州界 也就是與不毛大地的邊界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:54.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(416,328)}No Man's Land
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安裝有舊時代的監視設備 你們應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中三處是時候進行定期檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們在遠足的時候順便看看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 是遠足啊遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:17.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那東西壞了 我們也無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:24.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾克塔監視設備是完全的黑箱 無法分析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:24.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(396,328)}Black Box
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「武運昌盛」原來是指這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是悠哉悠哉地走路是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是要讓你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:50.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 這種情況要向前用力…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動…動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:12.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼不辜負我對你們的期待 大家真是群乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 要背重背包的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要往後倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把背包的重量完全架到背上後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了你們 快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:58.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N那麼我和菲莉西婭先繞到地圖上標好的終點 等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得不行了 就吹喇叭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:05.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會去找你們…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 這座山有野獸出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇上了可以任意應付 允許開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你們好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:07.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重 好重 好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮 別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越叫越覺得重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留 還有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留 叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動中 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 輕鬆地就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著這勢頭去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:28.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一想到它一直在這裡孤單地守護著城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 乃繪留 下一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來想想辦法搞定這個行李啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:42.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:48.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然隊長和梨旺前輩都討厭我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣 所以才這樣整我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你說句話啊 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話都不說句 真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下 彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:25.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼爽 真乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:57.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息 無論如何都要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:03.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 小暮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太沒緊張感了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是遠足嘛 得好好享受下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記那個重得要死的行李了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 菲莉西婭姐也說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該發覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:06.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人很黑 全身都是黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮白膚 很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是菲莉西婭的萌點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定看錯地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:28.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 誰來救救這對天然呆二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 吃午飯啦 吃·午·飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得濕漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天氣 馬上就干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糧食 沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:55.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鄉下也經常有菜地被踐踏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:16:00.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過夏天有很多食物 一般都不會出沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南針沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 把行李扔在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:17.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 優先到達終點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的設備是這裡 河的位置在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:28.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進入了有第二個設備的山頂所在的山頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們只要往上爬就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 無論如何也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:40.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼能吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又甜又有點酸 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫得真響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過爬不上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應當趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:16.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯少校還試過三天三夜不吃不喝\N開著坦克橫越沙漠 擊破了敵人的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這程度 算不上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:24.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被稱為「沙漠之狼」 可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個克勞斯叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們繼續努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的楊梅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個 發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後那個在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都黑下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:24.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為邊詳細確認方向邊走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「應該」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有指南針不能完全保證正確
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走到這裡 都白費了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:43.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這麼重要的指南針 你應該放好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啊 不要在這樣的地方吵架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 不應該在河邊悠哉悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:55.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 你完全不知道什麼叫緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:03.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都嘿嘿笑發大傻\N就因為你這個樣子才會搞得這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 船到橋頭自然直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達終點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 到了啊 小暮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我知道了 放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不毛大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\pos(318,328)}No Man's Land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:43.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人間的邊際
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:58.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說遠足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:06.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想讓你們看一看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的前輩的簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:14.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞的少女都至少來過這裡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後都看過這個風景…看過世界的邊際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…歷史吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能走一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:37.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一處前輩們留下的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺…前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 那傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:21.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也沒有白辛苦
